ing-transform)\">Vier routes naar vestiging in Paraguay</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-[var(--text-light)]\">Kies het programma dat bij uw doel past. Altijd transparante prijs en professionele begeleiding.</p></div><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-6\" style=\"grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr))\" data-cols=\"4\"><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-2\"><article class=\"relative flex h-full flex-col rounded-lg border p-8 transition-all border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Paraguay Base</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-light)]\">Paraguayaanse verblijfsvergunning en identiteitskaart.</p><div class=\"mt-6\"><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)]\">Nader te bepalen</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\">LEALTIS-groothandelskosten in afwachting + Nexa-marge</p></div><ul class=\"mt-6 flex-1 space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Paraguayaanse verblijfsvergunning</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Identiteitskaart</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Documentanalyse vooraf</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Operationele dag (één dag)</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Logistieke begeleiding</span></li></ul><a href=\"/s/nl/nexa-paraguay/contacto?programa=base\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium transition-all duration-normal focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 border-2 border-[var(--secondary)] text-[var(--secondary)] bg-transparent hover:bg-[var(--secondary)] hover:text-white h-13 px-8 text-lg rounded-lg mt-8 w-full\">Consult aanvragen</a></article></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-3\"><article class=\"relative flex h-full flex-col rounded-lg border p-8 transition-all border-[var(--secondary)] bg-[var(--surface)] shadow-card-hover\"><span class=\"absolute -top-3 left-6 rounded-full bg-[var(--secondary)] px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--secondary-foreground)]\">Meest gekozen</span><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Paraguay Business</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-light)]\">Verblijfsvergunning + vennootschap + bankrekening.</p><div class=\"mt-6\"><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)]\">USD 4.400+</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\">LEALTIS-basisprijs. Definitieve Nexa-prijs nog te bepalen.</p></div><ul class=\"mt-6 flex-1 space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Alles van Base</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Oprichting vennootschap</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>RUC-registratie</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Opening zakelijke bankrekening</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Strategische vastgoedrondleiding</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Honoraria, btw en leges inbegrepen</span></li></ul><a href=\"/s/nl/nexa-paraguay/contacto?programa=business\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium transition-all duration-normal focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-[var(--secondary)] text-white shadow-button hover:shadow-card-hover hover:-translate-y-0.5 h-13 px-8 text-lg rounded-lg mt-8 w-full\">Consult aanvragen</a></article></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-4\"><article class=\"relative flex h-full flex-col rounded-lg border p-8 transition-all border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Paraguay Investor Program</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-light)]\">Alles van Business + 12 maanden begeleiding.</p><div class=\"mt-6\"><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)]\">USD 6.900+</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\">LEALTIS-basisprijs. Definitieve Nexa-prijs nog te bepalen.</p></div><ul class=\"mt-6 flex-1 space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Alles van Business</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Boekhouding (12 maanden)</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Juridisch en fiscaal advies (12 maanden)</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Investeringsanalyse</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Directe toegang tot het technische team</span></li></ul><a href=\"/s/nl/nexa-paraguay/contacto?programa=investor\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium transition-all duration-normal focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 border-2 border-[var(--secondary)] text-[var(--secondary)] bg-transparent hover:bg-[var(--secondary)] hover:text-white h-13 px-8 text-lg rounded-lg mt-8 w-full\">Consult aanvragen</a></article></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-5\"><article class=\"relative flex h-full flex-col rounded-lg border p-8 transition-all border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Grondaankoop</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-light)]\">Eigen dienst van Nexa. Integraal advies.</p><div class=\"mt-6\"><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)]\">Nader te bepalen</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Scope en prijzen in ontwikkeling.</p></div><ul class=\"mt-6 flex-1 space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Profiel- en criteriadefinitie</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Zoektocht en shortlist</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Juridische en technische due diligence</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Onderhandeling en notariële akte</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Registratie in het kadaster</span></li></ul><a href=\"/s/nl/nexa-paraguay/contacto?programa=tierras\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium transition-all duration-normal focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 border-2 border-[var(--secondary)] text-[var(--secondary)] bg-transparent hover:bg-[var(--secondary)] hover:text-white h-13 px-8 text-lg rounded-lg mt-8 w-full\">Verkennend gesprek</a></article></div></div></div></section><section id=\"por-que\" class=\"bg-[var(--background)] py-16 sm:py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"animate-on-scroll mb-12 text-center\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--secondary)]\">Waarom Paraguay</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl leading-tight font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--text)]\" style=\"text-transform:var(--heading-transform)\">Een reële kans voor de Europese investeerder</h2></div><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-2\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-8 shadow-card transition-all hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-[var(--secondary)]/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Economisch klimaat</h3><p class=\"text-[var(--text-light)]\">Gestage groei, beheerste inflatie, 10% inkomstenbelasting, territoriaal systeem.</p><ul class=\"mt-4 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Vennootschapsbelasting 10%</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Territoriaal systeem</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Open economie</span></li></ul></article></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-3\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-8 shadow-card transition-all hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-[var(--secondary)]/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 8h4\"></path><path d=\"M14 21v-3a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v3\"></path><path d=\"M6 10H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 21V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Investeringskansen</h3><p class=\"text-[var(--text-light)]\">Groeiende vastgoedmarkt, sterke landbouwindustrie, open economie.</p><ul class=\"mt-4 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Groeiend vastgoed</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Toonaangevende agroindustrie</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Jong ondernemersklimaat</span></li></ul></article></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-4\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-8 shadow-card transition-all hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-[var(--secondary)]/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Levenskwaliteit</h3><p class=\"text-[var(--text-light)]\">Warm klimaat, groeiende internationale gemeenschap, aanzienlijke koopkracht.</p><ul class=\"mt-4 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Gunstige levenskosten</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Internationale community</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Persoonlijke veiligheid</span></li></ul></article></div></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll\"><aside class=\"mx-auto mt-12 max-w-3xl rounded-lg border-l-4 border-[var(--secondary)] bg-[var(--surface-light)] p-6\"><p class=\"text-sm italic text-[var(--text-light)]\">De kans is reëel, maar het proces is niet eenvoudig zonder goede begeleiding. Daar zijn wij voor.</p></aside></div></div></section><section id=\"proceso\" class=\"bg-[var(--surface-light)] py-16 sm:py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"animate-on-scroll mb-12 text-center\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--secondary)]\">Hoe het werkt</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl leading-tight font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--text)]\" style=\"text-transform:var(--heading-transform)\">Een helder proces, stap voor stap</h2></div><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-5\"><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-2\"><div class=\"relative text-center\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--secondary)] bg-[var(--surface)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.992 16.342a2 2 0 0 1 .094 1.167l-1.065 3.29a1 1 0 0 0 1.236 1.168l3.413-.998a2 2 0 0 1 1.099.092 10 10 0 1 0-4.777-4.719\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Eerste consult</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--text-light)]\">We bespreken uw situatie, doelen en het passende programma.</p></div></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-3\"><div class=\"relative text-center\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--secondary)] bg-[var(--surface)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-check text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"m9 15 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Documentvalidatie</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--text-light)]\">Alles wordt vooraf door ons team geverifieerd. U reist pas als alles klopt.</p></div></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-4\"><div class=\"relative text-center\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--secondary)] bg-[var(--surface)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Operationele dag</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--text-light)]\">In één dag voeren we alle persoonlijke afhandelingen uit.</p></div></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-5\"><div class=\"relative text-center\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--secondary)] bg-[var(--surface)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 10h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 6h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 10h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 6h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 10h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 6h.01\"></path><path d=\"M9 22v-3a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3\"></path><rect x=\"4\" y=\"2\" width=\"16\" height=\"20\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Vennootschap en bank</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--text-light)]\">Wij richten uw vennootschap op en coördineren de bankopening.</p></div></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-6\"><div class=\"relative text-center\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--secondary)] bg-[var(--surface)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Oplevering en nazorg</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--text-light)]\">U ontvangt de definitieve documenten en we sluiten het programma af.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 flex flex-col items-center gap-3 text-center\"><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Verwachte totale doorlooptijd: 8–12 weken.</p><a href=\"/s/nl/nexa-paraguay/contacto\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-[var(--secondary)] px-6 py-3 text-[var(--secondary-foreground)] shadow-button transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5\">Start mijn traject</a></div></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden py-16\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary) 0%, var(--primary) 100%)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.06]\" style=\"background-image:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 40%, rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 0%, transparent 50%)\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl relative z-10 text-center\"><div class=\"animate-on-scroll\"><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--secondary-foreground)] sm:text-4xl\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Zet de eerste stap</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl text-lg text-[var(--secondary-foreground)] opacity-80\">Plan een gratis consult van 30 minuten.</p><a href=\"/s/nl/nexa-paraguay/contacto\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium transition-all duration-normal focus-visible: